trans-unit.source: Represents a key identifier clause that identifies a <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken"></xref> or <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"></xref> security token.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en nøkkel-ID-setningsdel som identifiserer en <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"> </xref> sikkerhetskode.

trans-unit.source: Use the KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause class to reference a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken> or <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken> security token using a SHA-1 hash of the Kerberos ticket.
trans-unit.target: Bruk KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause klassen for å referere til en <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken>eller <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken>sikkerhetskode ved hjelp av et SHA-1-nummer for Kerberos-billetten.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: The SHA-1 hash of the Kerberos ticket can be obtained by calling the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause.GetKerberosTicketHash%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Kan hente SHA-1 hash-koden for Kerberos-billetten ved å kalle den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause.GetKerberosTicketHash%2A>metoden.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause.GetKerberosTicketHash%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause"></xref> class using the specified SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av angitte SHA-1 hash-koden for en billett for Kerberos-tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.Byte>som inneholder SHA-1 hash-koden for en Kerberos tjenestebillett.</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause"></xref> class using the specified Kerberos ticket, nonce, and key length.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosTicketHashKeyIdentifierClause"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av den angitte Kerberos-billetten midlertidig og nøkkellengde.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[vsindigo](~/add/includes/vsindigo-md.md)] does not support the creation of implied derived key identifiers.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[vsindigo](~/add/includes/vsindigo-md.md)] støtter ikke oppretting av implisitte identifikatorer av avledede.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[vsindigo](~/add/includes/vsindigo-md.md)] processes and consumes incoming SOAP messages that contain implied derived key identifiers.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid [!INCLUDE[vsindigo](~/add/includes/vsindigo-md.md)] behandler og forbruker innkommende SOAP-meldinger som inneholder implisitte identifikatorer av avledede.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.Byte>som inneholder SHA-1 hash-koden for en Kerberos tjenestebillett.</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the nonce that was used to create a derived key.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.Byte>som inneholder den midlertidige IDen som ble brukt til å opprette en avledet nøkkel.</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: The size of the derived key.
Gets the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: Henter SHA-1 hash-koden for en billett for Kerberos-tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Byte> that contains the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.Byte>som inneholder SHA-1 hash-koden for en Kerberos tjenestebillett.</xref:System.Byte>

trans-unit.source: The ToString method returns the SHA-1 hash of a Kerberos service ticket.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ToString returnerer SHA-1 hash-koden for en billett for Kerberos-tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the current object.
